  },
  {
    "id": "32",
    "idName": "jins_yegah",
    "name": "jins yegāh",
    "noteNames": [
      "yegāh",
      "ʿushayrān",
      "ʿirāq",
      "rāst"
    ],
    "commentsEnglish": "al-Ḥilū pairs this with jins rāst, the two differing only in their qarār, which here is yegāh.",
    "commentsArabic": "يقرنه الحلو بجنس الراست، ولا يختلفان إلا في درجة الاستقرار وهي هنا اليكاه.",
    "sourcePageReferences": [
